node.text:
Glam with nowhere to go, but I'm living for it! 🌟 I'm having SO much fun with this new product drop from @anastasiabeverlyhills #ad 💎 Brow Freeze 💎 styling wax makes styling your brows so easy!✨ "Iced Out" Highlighter ✨ leaves the ultimate finishing touch - a golden shimmer that looks lit-from-within. 💎 Diamond Gloss in shade Honey Diamond 💎 leaves a super glassy shine and reflective sparkle - but isn’t sticky at all!
-
music by @davinamichelleofficial x @woodiesmalls “Big Brother”

node.text:
this week at the UN, report on Sexual Orientation and Gender Identity was discussed in the Human Rights Council. 

as a 🇳🇱 UN Goodwill Ambassador, I’d like to speak from my own experience and want to share the following: We should have ZERO tolerance on delaying equal #HumanRights for all. 💖

node.title: using my platform for the good 💙

node.text: after so many of you asked for a hair tutorial I decided to film one for you today! 🤭😍❤️ make sure you tag me in any recreations! makeup is my comfort zone, so doing this on camera was SO SCARY... go easy on me haha. also, @bradmondonyc I hope I did okay.

node.text:
PAY IT NO MIND 🏳️‍⚧️ when I got asked to join the Met Gala(!!!!!) I knew I wanted to pay homage to a trans icon who was at the forefront of the Stonewall Riots… Marsha P. Johnson paved the way for so many of us, and I hope I made my community proud tonight 🥺 this night has been so incredibly surreal…. I can’t wait to tell you EVERYTHING!!!!!! 💕 WE DID IT GUYS!!!!!!!! thank you so much @youtube & @derekblasberg for this insane night.. I’ll forever be so grateful!
-
Products Used:  @maybelline + @nimya 
Hair: @mandynijland + @davidlopezzz 
Nails: @electanailart 
Styling: @marjabennenbroek 
Styling assist: @brandonmgarr
Dress: @edwin_oudshoorn

node.text: my OWN BRAND @nimya 🧡💙 I really can’t believe the word is out. almost three years ago now, I finally thought: why don’t I give this a shot? for the longest time I was too scared to dive in, but baby we’re about to DO THE DAMN THING!! 😅 thank you so much for your overwhelming love so far… you’re making it feel like I made the right decision 🥺😮‍💨💕
